{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-guide-js","path":"/styling","webpackCompilationHash":"19200969f43f11be1de4","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"styling-in-react\"><a href=\"#styling-in-react\" aria-label=\"styling in react permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Styling in React</h1>\n<p>This guide will introduce you to various approaches to styling when you use React.</p>\n<h2 id=\"inline-styles\"><a href=\"#inline-styles\" aria-label=\"inline styles permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Inline styles</h2>\n<pre class=\"default-dark vscode-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><code class=\"vscode-highlight-code\"><span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">const</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">headingStyle</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = {</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk12\">color:</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&#39;red&#39;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk12\">fontSize</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: </span><span class=\"mtk7\">30</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\">}</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">const</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk11\">Hello</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = () </span><span class=\"mtk4\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> (</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk17\">&lt;</span><span class=\"mtk4\">h1</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">style</span><span class=\"mtk1\">=</span><span class=\"mtk4\">{</span><span class=\"mtk12\">headingStyle</span><span class=\"mtk4\">}</span><span class=\"mtk17\">&gt;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">Hello</span><span class=\"mtk17\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk4\">h1</span><span class=\"mtk17\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\">)</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>It's possible to use the <code>style</code> prop to apply styles. Note that keys must be camelCased. We use <code>fontSize</code> and not <code>font-size</code>. <code>px</code> is added to <em>most</em> (exceptions can be found <a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/react/blob/4131af3e4bf52f3a003537ec95a1655147c81270/src/renderers/dom/shared/CSSProperty.js#L15-L59\">here</a>) numerical values, thus the font-size will <code>30px</code>.</p>\n<p>Note that it is not recommended to use inline styles due to poorer performance compared to other approaches and lack of automatic support of older browsers.</p>\n<h2 id=\"plain-css\"><a href=\"#plain-css\" aria-label=\"plain css permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Plain CSS</h2>\n<pre class=\"default-dark vscode-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><code class=\"vscode-highlight-code\"><span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk3\">/* style.css */</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk6\">h1</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> {</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk12\">color</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: </span><span class=\"mtk8\">red</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk12\">font-size</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: </span><span class=\"mtk7\">30px</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\">}</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk6\">.blue</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> {</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk12\">color</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: </span><span class=\"mtk8\">blue</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\">}</span></span></code></pre>\n<pre class=\"default-dark vscode-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><code class=\"vscode-highlight-code\"><span class=\"vscode-highlight-line vscode-highlight-line-highlighted\"><span class=\"mtk15\">import</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&#39;./style.css&#39;</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">const</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk11\">Hello</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = () </span><span class=\"mtk4\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk17\">&lt;</span><span class=\"mtk4\">h1</span><span class=\"mtk17\">&gt;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">Hello</span><span class=\"mtk17\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk4\">h1</span><span class=\"mtk17\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">const</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk11\">Hi</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = () </span><span class=\"mtk4\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> (</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line vscode-highlight-line-highlighted\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk17\">&lt;</span><span class=\"mtk4\">span</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">className</span><span class=\"mtk1\">=</span><span class=\"mtk4\">{</span><span class=\"mtk12\">blue</span><span class=\"mtk4\">}</span><span class=\"mtk17\">&gt;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">hi</span><span class=\"mtk17\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk4\">span</span><span class=\"mtk17\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\">)</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>You can import CSS files in JavaScript files. Notice that we use <code>className</code> and not <code>class</code>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"styled-components\"><a href=\"#styled-components\" aria-label=\"styled components permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>styled-components</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.styled-components.com/\">styled-components</a> is one of several libraries created for styling in React. Other popular alternatives include <a href=\"https://emotion.sh/docs/introduction\">Emotion</a> and <a href=\"https://github.com/zeit/styled-jsx\">Styled JSX</a>.</p>\n<h3 id=\"creating-components\"><a href=\"#creating-components\" aria-label=\"creating components permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Creating components</h3>\n<p>You can create React components by using <code>styled</code>. The syntax is exactly the same as if you were to write CSS. The CSS rules are scoped within the component, which means that for the below example, any other <code>h1</code> elements will not be affected. The CSS rules are also automatically vendor-prefixed, meaning that rules are created to work in different browsers. </p>\n<pre class=\"default-dark vscode-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><code class=\"vscode-highlight-code\"><span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk15\">import</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">styled</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk15\">from</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&#39;styled-components&#39;</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">const</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">Heading</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk12\">styled</span><span class=\"mtk8\">.</span><span class=\"mtk11\">h1</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&#96;</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk8\">  color: red;</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk8\">  font-size: 30px;</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk8\">&#96;</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">const</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk11\">Hello</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = () </span><span class=\"mtk4\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk17\">&lt;</span><span class=\"mtk10\">Heading</span><span class=\"mtk17\">&gt;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">Hello</span><span class=\"mtk17\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk10\">Heading</span><span class=\"mtk17\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"applying-styles-to-components\"><a href=\"#applying-styles-to-components\" aria-label=\"applying styles to components permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Applying styles to components</h3>\n<p>You can also apply styles <em>to</em> any React component that apply the <code>className</code> prop. Notice how we use <code>styled()</code> for components, and not <code>styled.</code> as we did with <code>h1</code>.</p>\n<pre class=\"default-dark vscode-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><code class=\"vscode-highlight-code\"><span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk15\">import</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">styled</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk15\">from</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&#39;styled-components&#39;</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">const</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">BlueHello</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk11\">styled</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk12\">Hello</span><span class=\"mtk1\">)</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&#96;</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk8\">  color: red;</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk8\">  font-size: 30px;</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk8\">&#96;</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">const</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk11\">Hello</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = ({ </span><span class=\"mtk12\">className</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> }) </span><span class=\"mtk4\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> (</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk17\">&lt;</span><span class=\"mtk4\">h1</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">className</span><span class=\"mtk1\">=</span><span class=\"mtk4\">{</span><span class=\"mtk12\">className</span><span class=\"mtk4\">}</span><span class=\"mtk17\">&gt;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">Hello</span><span class=\"mtk17\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk4\">h1</span><span class=\"mtk17\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\">)</span></span></code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"styling-dhis2-components\"><a href=\"#styling-dhis2-components\" aria-label=\"styling dhis2 components permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Styling DHIS2 components</h3>\n<p>The components in <a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/@dhis2/ui-core\">@dhis2/ui-core</a> and <a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/@dhis2/ui-widgets\">@dhis2/ui-widgets</a> accept the <code>className</code> prop, meaning you can use styled-components.</p>\n<pre class=\"default-dark vscode-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><code class=\"vscode-highlight-code\"><span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk15\">import</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">styled</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk15\">from</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&#39;styled-components&#39;</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk15\">import</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> { </span><span class=\"mtk12\">HeaderBar</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> } </span><span class=\"mtk15\">from</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&#39;@dhis2/ui-widgets&#39;</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">const</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">FixedHeaderBar</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk11\">styled</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk12\">HeaderBar</span><span class=\"mtk1\">)</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&#96;</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk8\">  position: fixed;</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk8\">  width: 100%;</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk8\">  z-index: 1000;</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk8\">  top: 0;</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk8\">&#96;</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>Note that you have to use <code>!important</code> when you want to override CSS rules already set by a component.</p>\n<pre class=\"default-dark vscode-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><code class=\"vscode-highlight-code\"><span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk15\">import</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">styled</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk15\">from</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&#39;styled-components&#39;</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk15\">import</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> { </span><span class=\"mtk12\">Card</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> } </span><span class=\"mtk15\">from</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&#39;@dhis2/ui-core&#39;</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">const</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">FixedHeaderBar</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk11\">styled</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk12\">Card</span><span class=\"mtk1\">)</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&#96;</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk8\">  width: 50% !important;</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk8\">&#96;</span></span></code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"props\"><a href=\"#props\" aria-label=\"props permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Props</h3>\n<p>The components accept props.</p>\n<pre class=\"default-dark vscode-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><code class=\"vscode-highlight-code\"><span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk15\">import</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">styled</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk15\">from</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&#39;styled-components&#39;</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">const</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">ColoredSpan</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk12\">styled</span><span class=\"mtk8\">.</span><span class=\"mtk11\">span</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&#96;</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk8\">  color: </span><span class=\"mtk4\">${</span><span class=\"mtk12\">props</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk4\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">props</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk12\">color</span><span class=\"mtk4\">}</span><span class=\"mtk8\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk8\">&#96;</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-high